Text: Pictures reportso much for all the goodies We really enjoyed the pictures Arent cats all alike in wanting to get into enclosures I believe that was the first picture we have seen of her We would really like to have a hard copy of that picture of you Can that be done The analysts report prompted me to get on the stick and send off some more money to the direct purchase plan of Enron stock The online trading platform that was mentioned in the reportis that what you were involved in launching and about which you are continuing to answer questions We are sending your birthday package to your office by UPS today so you can start looking for it about Wednesday I guess Love Mother
